II. 🎯 Product Definition

Inner Atlas is the first implementation of the
Embodied Tensor Interface (ETI):

A system that allows users to map internal states onto a structured body model, track changes over time, and extract meaningful patterns.

⸻

III. 🧠 Core Insight (Compressed)

InnerAtlas:
  replaces: text-based self tracking
  with: spatial + temporal self mapping
  result: intuition-speed understanding of patterns


⸻

IV. 🧬 Product Pillars

1. Embodiment
	•	Data lives on the body, not in forms
	•	“Where” matters as much as “what”

2. Temporal Awareness
	•	Snapshots → timelines → deltas
	•	You don’t just log—you watch change

3. Pattern Emergence
	•	Clusters, correlations, recurrence
	•	Insight comes from structure, not analysis alone

4. Interpretability First
	•	Human-readable before AI-optimized
	•	Geometry > text

